{"tid":2240073,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］磁力懸浮床有冇得諗","createTime":"2020-10-12T11:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T03:31:35.000Z","uid":300420,"like":10,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bb73228cb2621a6b7337f5e2df8948e8e1e1df40","tid":2240073,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"講吓我啲嘢先<br />\n小弟成日受到腰背痛困擾<br />\n每日起身個背脊都好僵硬又酸病<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先做完assignment之後鳩上網搵嘢睇 俾我睇到磁浮列車嘅原理<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCbd8mA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCbd8mA.gif&h=be01b9a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰一下我睇到解決腰背痛嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最新構思 - 磁力懸浮床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實就係一舊小型電磁鐵盒仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要人着上一件綁住電磁鐵嘅衫 再瞓入去嗰張通咗電嘅磁力懸浮床度 佢就可以浮起訓覺 <br />\n仲可以轉呀轉 轉呀轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後唔使再擔心腰酸背痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oAW9GKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoAW9GKA.jpg&h=31be4243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果呢個技術可以用係長期臥床嘅病人度 就可以完全避免褥瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有巴絲打出資畀我研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">利申：冇讀過physics<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"65ed84ea98cef8dfb96cbc5fd39fcb9a6a584873","tid":2240073,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a58ab006be87754af5f2f3220e6508793444ade","tid":2240073,"uid":135390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"咁你要全身包到實晒先可以喎<br />\n如果唔係你露出黎d手手腳腳就會條條揈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f81057d1764b75a8b99e445696c9be62d7999e8","tid":2240073,"uid":300420,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a58ab006be87754af5f2f3220e6508793444ade","tid":2240073,"uid":135390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"咁你要全身包到實晒先可以喎<br />\n如果唔係你露出黎d手手腳腳就會條條揈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"可以搵條繩吊住啲手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5364a4d218b5f065debe09ffe6cf92930d910360","tid":2240073,"uid":135390,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9f81057d1764b75a8b99e445696c9be62d7999e8","tid":2240073,"uid":300420,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a58ab006be87754af5f2f3220e6508793444ade","tid":2240073,"uid":135390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"咁你要全身包到實晒先可以喎<br />\n如果唔係你露出黎d手手腳腳就會條條揈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"可以搵條繩吊住啲手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"咁咪仲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f199d7d4fabaf519321c2637483811bb1465460","tid":2240073,"uid":11067,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:54:55.000